body:
No idea why @iSazonov 's [MR](https://github.com/PowerShell/PowerShell/pull/11397) was closed, but per @mklement0 's suggestion, I just changed the `parsedJson` from `JObject` to `JToken` and everything works with just one line of diff (plus one to remove unnecessary outside declaration):

```csharp
-                parsedJson = JObject.Parse(Json);
+                var parsedJson = JToken.Parse(Json);
```

I'll add extra tests and create an MR.
